<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>입출고 내역 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex">
  {{> common/sidebar-item-manager}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="content-wrapper flex-1 p-6">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
            <i data-feather="clock" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">물품 입출고 내역</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">모든 물품의 입고 및 출고 기록을 확인합니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <i data-feather="clock" class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-400"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">입출고 내역 기능 준비 중</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">입출고 이력 관리 기능은 추후 제공될 예정입니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>feather.replace();</script>
</body>
</html>
